<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>A class to manage the OLED screen using Adafruit_SSD1306 library. </para>



<para>This class provides methods to initialize, clear, and print text on the screen.</para>

<para><note><title>Note</title>

<para>Inherits from Adafruit_SSD1306. </para>
</note>
</para>
</section>
